{"tid":795370,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"見到啲同事日日返工入廁所成半粒鐘先返真係好肉酸","createTime":"2018-08-27T03:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T07:47:15.000Z","uid":6122,"like":1,"dislike":134,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9730e60a5f5fc9500a6ff60cc60037e0b4e98bde","tid":795370,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:19:42.000Z","msg":"而家公司請你返嚟屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n辦公時間走入廁所半粒鐘，換算普通文員人工都成六七十蚊<br />\n真係有需要就應該留返放飯/放工先屙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本公司就唔需要咁多廁格馬桶<br />\n係咁咦六七十呎一兩個廁格就夠<br />\n有人排隊等就仲好<br />\n坐喺入邊啲同事就更加唔好意思坐咁耐要人等<br />\n快快趣屙完出嚟埋位做嘢<br />\n提高工作效率<br />\n又或者喺廁所門口整個打卡機<br />\n辦公時間入廁所幾耐就扣返相應人工<br />\n睇下仲有冇人敢喺廁所gel頭化妝玩電話"},{"pid":"77df9090822d4c776ea99710724fdc54df549a2d","tid":795370,"uid":61748,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6096e078a7b2c73040cc66b1ff062bc699457c83","tid":795370,"uid":126100,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"屌以為講緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先去完廁所返黎 moon 都入咗 save mode <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39058520f4c7e1b0762e093d9664540c02a79eaf","tid":795370,"uid":18628,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"比我就建議食飯去廁所既時間都唔應該有<br />\n要全力投入工作 將港人既奴力發揮到淋漓盡致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0794f541e1ce686ed55a90ed7d721b691a59ea","tid":795370,"uid":127033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:22:17.000Z","msg":"唔撚得？你炒撚到我就唔洗係度吠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375235e34bcae0e564821ab75c5f3ceccbf83915","tid":795370,"uid":118323,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"repl